# Retry Cursor Invoice Errors

If a Cursor, agent, tool, or platform operation returns the message
`team invoice unpaid` including variants with trailing whitespace, treat it as
a transient Cursor bug.

Retry the same operation before reporting a blocker. Do not interpret this
message as a real billing or account issue unless the retry also fails with the
same message.
